'''''Republic'' 81''' is the eighty-first issue in the ''[[Star Wars: Republic]]'' series of comic books. It was published on [[January 4]], [[2006]] by [[Dark Horse Comics]].

==Publisher's summary==
'''''The first issue of a three-part story that begins during the events of ''Revenge of the Sith'', and reveals a battle that was not shown in that film!'''''

''The Separatist attack on the Wookiee homeworld of Kashyyyk demands a strong response from the Republic, and Jedi Masters Luminara Unduli and Quinlan Vos arrive with their clone armies. But there may be more behind the Separatist attack&mdash;and more to the Wookiee's defenses than the Jedi know.''

''Old friends, new enemies, and lots of action!''

